java.lang.Object

java.io.Serializable
public class Definition
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

The Definition of a ContextSpecification, including the name, and a instanceOf String, providing a reference to the type of context.

The Context Definition also contains arrays of Attribute properties, and Members.

Michael Crouch
